CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

October 23, 2002

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2002-1421. State ex rel. Joseph & Joseph v. Watson.

In Mandamus. On answer of respondent and amended motion for judgment on pleadings. On S.Ct.Prac.R. X(5) determination, cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
